Class Circle

  • java.lang.Object
    • Shape
      • Circle

  • public class Circle
extends Shape
    A Circle is a Shape that maintains information about its radius. A Circle knows how to return its radius, set its radius, calculate and return its area, and calculate and return its circumference.
